  "description": "This individual is a middle-aged human of taupe skin, carrying the compact, well-fed build common to settled traders who spend more time counting measures than hauling them. Brown eyes sit beneath heavy lids and a square brow, giving the face a habitually appraising cast. Brown hair, worn in a parted style, is kept close and orderly, and a trimmed beard frames a jaw broadened by age. The hands are thick-fingered and ink-stained, with small nicks at the knuckles consistent with years of tying cords, opening crates, and handling coin.",
